{"tid":2511283,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–痴肥對癌症腫瘤生長的影響","createTime":"2021-04-30T19:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T19:38:08.000Z","uid":38861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5faaf1126c4d4b079b7a6cb2b64ae6f50b398f","tid":2511283,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:28:15.000Z","msg":"痴肥人士的患癌風險及死亡率均比健康人士為高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdjhCD2k4xNvg9dAqccmtngxGWW43hj6giuCiFDuoqq8q?filename=x9wbdb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9wbdb0.jpg&h=7b5ae7bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位於癌細胞在所位置附近的肥肪細胞，相信亦有份協助癌細胞助大的進程。<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)從圖中的老鼠動物模型中可見，痴肥老鼠的腫瘤體積明顯比正常老鼠的為大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZFVGgQwHXqMf7iiHUCKmdHcqeMQiuCYuJ993nkvoPMFv?filename=CygOfqo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCygOfqo.png&h=030a6198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n痴肥老鼠的整體體重比正常老鼠的為重，雙方的肌肉重量並無太分別，唯痴肥老鼠的脂肪重量明顯比正常老鼠的為重。<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)經過一系列的研究後，科學家發現脂肪細胞會供應Creatine給癌細胞，促進其生長。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXMNxCtq5Cv5VhL83FLpTyNk2BeU2SLgjCw5sxcqJPPnM?filename=8a6RXDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8a6RXDL.png&h=ef80518b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果剔除<span class=\"blue\">脂肪細胞其中一隻負責製造Creatine的蛋白酶</span>、或者剔除<span class=\"red\">癌細胞表面負責攝取Creatine的蛋白酶</span>，雖並不會對老鼠整體重量有大影響，但可以清楚得到痴肥老鼠腫瘤的縮細;<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">這效果只有在痴肥老鼠上才會出現，剔除相關的基因並沒有對健康老鼠的腫瘤體積有任何大影響。</span><br />\n<br />\n重要的是，就算在老鼠餐單上加入大量Creatine，亦不會對腫瘤重量有影響，這亦表明了只有癌細胞旁脂肪細胞所供應的本土Creatine才會對腫瘤的發展有正面影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=8bbd50b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=cfb911cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/cell-metabolism/fulltext/S1550-4131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcell-metabolism%2Ffulltext%2FS1550-4131&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=42d2c259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/cell-metabolism/fulltext/S1550-4131</a>(21)00056-5"},{"pid":"5dea5d6f71d08fa3b7b08336ee0736274a30975a","tid":2511283,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"96a0dfdc86d904b555e2fec87383f9eb91b55a8d","tid":2511283,"uid":393797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:30:37.000Z","msg":"又學到野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝"},{"pid":"07d77b33817737d2cf59b0087724e7c9aa85606a","tid":2511283,"uid":171561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:33:21.000Z","msg":"重要的是，就算在老鼠餐單上加入大量Creatine，亦不會對腫瘤重量有影響<br />\n<br />\n好撚彩 gym撚有食開creatine 睇頭半段嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1341d8c002e88661c0ee3bee80af66326841937a","tid":2511283,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:33:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5dec3803aeee57ca18c774d019b1182ed15d190","tid":2511283,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:33:45.000Z","msg":"sor唔小心不推左"},{"pid":"de476c900dc8b14c148e3fa423318a44cf763ec3","tid":2511283,"uid":109560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:37:45.000Z","msg":"食脂肪又供應creatine，食碳水又有葡萄糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be747612305906e30a7b8dd2e76742eff4dd8ceb","tid":2511283,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:38:08.000Z","msg":"其實癌細胞係以糖定蛋白質定係脂肪做&quot;食糧&quot;🤔"}]}